<DIV ALIGN=CENTER><h1>Panhandle Pizza</h1></DIV>
<IMG VSPACE=0 HSPACE=8 SRC="dot_clear.gif">While Panhandle 
Pizza is without question the smallest establishment on our list of best bets, 
it turns out pizzas with a cornmeal crust that is among the best found 
anywhere outside my own kitchen.  "Cornmeal?" you may ask.  That's right.  
Not everyone is fortunate to have a wood-fired oven, but a bit of cornmeal in 
pizza dough gives it both texture and depth of flavor, and Panhandle does it 
well.  Add a pizza sauce with a nice bite and three flavorful cheeses, and 
your Inner Richmond trip is easily justified.
<BR>
<BR>
